formly from any pre-image. By the connection in [CG14b],\nwe also obtain the first explicit non-malleable codes with tampering degree $t$\nup to $n^{\\Omega(1)}$, relative rate $n^{\\Omega(1)}/n$, and error\n$2^{-n^{\\Omega(1)}}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 1 May 2015 07:18:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-04"}
